race.comment: FLASH BANDIT (2) ran a nice race two back to fill a minor placing then got off the mark last time (20.75) at Nowra over 365m. Drawn well off an inside draw. Maiden this journey but has some solid runs behind her. Tougher here but can go on with it. FAST JENNY (1) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but ran over late and missed the frame when a 1.5 lengths fourth (21.09) over 365m at Nowra. Leading chance. CAWBOURNE MAXX (4) ran below best last time finishing seventh (25.93) over 440m at this track in a Grade 5. Should be about the money. RUE DEVILLE (8) will have admirers after placing last time out.
